GlusterFS Geo-replication provides an incremental replication service
over Local Area Networks (LANs), Wide Area Network (WANs), and across
the Internet. This section illustrates the most common deployment
scenarios for GlusterFS Geo-replication, including the following:

* Geo-replication over LAN
* Geo-replication over WAN
* Geo-replication over the Internet
* Multi-site cascading Geo-replication

 +
 *Geo-replication over LAN*

You can configure GlusterFS Geo-replication to mirror data over a Local
Area Network.

